        Pair<T,U> getChecked()
              throws java.lang.Exception
        PairSupplier.get() equivalent which declares a throws clauses, allowing exceptions to be caught outside of lambda context. Like other interfaces of this package, this interface implements a java corresponding interface. All exceptions which occurs inside the lambda is rethrown in the implemented method using RethrowException.rethrow(Throwable).
